rn-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2529428\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104kxz1665702827933.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kxz1665702827933.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kxz1665702827933.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"kxz1665702827933\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                          \n Define Drop-down List Properties (Character Mode)\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Define the properties of this drop-down list when it appears in character mode.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kxz1665702827933__p_d8972e1_d8973e1_d8974e1\">For more information about drop-down lists, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fud1688450548955.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fud1688450548955.html\" title=\"The udropdownlist widget is a field-level widget that can display a list of valid options in a list below the input field, so that the user can select one. It is applicable only to form components.\">udropdownlist (DropDownList)</a>.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kxz1665702827933__section_mrg_pck_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d788200e64\">Properties</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"kxz1665702827933__ul_ycl_pck_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kxz1665702827933__li_d4094e1_d4095e1_d4096e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hqe1665702630313.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hqe1665702630313.html\" title=\"Determines whether the items in this widget are sorted alphabetically when displayed at run time. True or False (default)\">Sort Alphabetically</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kxz1665702827933__li_d4097e1_d4098e1_d4099e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rmk1665702630446.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rmk1665702630446.html\" title=\"This widget supports the ValRep property. For convenience, you can edit the ValRep property of the field in the Widget Properties dialog, even though this is a field-level property rather than a widget property.\">Value and Representation</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kxz1665702827933__section_jg1_tck_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d788200e100\">How to</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kxz1665702827933__p_d9062e1_d9063e1_d9064e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mae1704708062818.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mae1704708062818.html\" title=\"You can set widget properties in several ways—in the initialization file used by the application, in the IDE using the Properties Inspector, or in script. And you can set them in modeled entities, in component templates, in components, and in script.\">Setting Widget Properties</a>\n</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nya1665702871383.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Widgets and Character Mode</a><p>If you create components that are intended for use in a character mode environment, be economical with the amount of text you display in each label and widget.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dhj1704361240115.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>ValRep Lists and Ranges</a><p>Fields have a ValRep property that can be used to define a limited range of possible values for that field.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529428\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529428\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Define Drop-down List Properties (Character Mode) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Define Drop-down List Properties (Character Mode) Define the properties of this drop-down list when it appears in character mode. For more information about drop-down lists, see udropdownlist (DropDownList) . Properties Sort Alphabetically Value and Representation How to Setting Widget Properties Related Links Widgets and Character Mode If you create components that are intended for use in a character mode environment, be economical with the amount of text you display in each label and widget. ValRep Lists and Ranges Fields have a ValRep property that can be used to define a limited range of possible values for that field. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}